looseglasscannons.description: Deadly but fragile bosses are everywhere!

TreasureHunt.description: Locke is a true Treasure Hunter and he is taking his friends Terra and Cyan on a chest finding adventure while the stores are closed

dragongifts.description: Vanquish dragons to reach Kefka's Tower! Each dragon offers a reward, but watch out - not all dragon gifts are worth receiving...

dragonhunt.description: A classic dragon hunt with an extra helping of dragoon flavour

clue.description: Complete objectives requiring combinations of randomly selected characters, espers, bosses, dragons, and quests. It was Colonel Mustard in the Library with… an Illumina? (Hint: The Track menu is your friend!)

fallout.description: Survive the post-apocalyptic wasteland, but watch out for mutated bosses, and be careful of checks in highly irradiated areas or you might get mutated as well!

dragonescalation.description: Slain dragons transfer their power to their remaining brethren. Can you defeat enough to reach Kefka before the last dragons become too powerful?
